public interface PartitionImmutableList<T>
extends PartitionImmutableCollection<T>, PartitionList<T>
A PartitionImmutableList is the result of splitting an immutable list into two immutable lists based on a Predicate. The results that answer true for the Predicate will be returned from the getSelected() method and the results that answer false for the predicate will be returned from the getRejected() method.
